WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.067 line:84% position:15% size:19%
Pop-on captions,

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.067 line:90% position:16% size:31%
pop on and off the screen.

00:00:03.067 --> 00:00:06.100 align:start line:90% position:14% size:32%
They are used with programs
with multiple characters.

00:00:06.100 --> 00:00:08.467 line:84% position:18% size:13%
They can be

00:00:06.100 --> 00:00:08.467 line:90% position:20% size:24%
strategically placed

00:00:08.467 --> 00:00:11.167 align:start line:90% position:14% size:33%
as to indicate to the viewer
who is speaking.

00:00:11.167 --> 00:00:12.400 align:start line:90% position:10% size:15%
For example,

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:13.633 align:start line:90% position:10% size:23%
if the person
is on the left side

00:00:13.633 --> 00:00:14.733 align:start line:90% position:10% size:16%
of the screen

00:00:14.733 --> 00:00:16.033 align:start line:90% position:10% size:23%
the pop-on captions
would appear

00:00:16.033 --> 00:00:17.600 align:start line:90% position:10% size:20%
on the left side.

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:18.967 line:84% position:23% size:13%
If they are

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:18.967 line:90% position:23% size:17%
in the middle,

00:00:18.967 --> 00:00:20.767 line:84% position:17% size:29%
the caption would appear

00:00:18.967 --> 00:00:20.767 line:90% position:16% size:17%
in the middle.

00:00:20.767 --> 00:00:22.333 line:84% position:32% size:22%
Or, if they are on

00:00:20.767 --> 00:00:22.333 line:90% position:31% size:17%
the right side

00:00:22.333 --> 00:00:23.567 line:90% position:38% size:16%
of the screen

00:00:23.567 --> 00:00:25.533 line:84% position:30% size:24%
caption would pop-on

00:00:23.567 --> 00:00:25.533 line:90% position:28% size:18%
the right side.

